    "content": "**STRICTLY PRIVATE LAYER (Source of Truth)**\n- user_framework_essence\n\n- user_framework_features\n\n- sessions (raw conversations)\n\n- conversations\n\n- reflection\n\n(These tables contain raw user data and are never exposed to other users.)\n**PRIVACY CONTROLLED LAYER**\n- door_private (all new doors start here)\n\n- memories\n\n- impression_object\n\n- impression_category\nThese maintain both private and public versions in same table, controlled by is_public flag. When a door card is made public, associated records are marked public through conversation_id.\n\n**PUBLIC INTERFACE LAYER**\n- door_public (doors that users choose to share)\n- memories (public version)\n- impression_object (public version)\n- impression_category (public version)\n- door_hero (pre-seeded content)\nControls what other users can see and interact with. Door cards act as the gateway for making content public.\n\n\n\n\n[[Core user flow]]",
